description: The North Fork Food Truck is mobile serving local and seasonal fare to visitors and residents of the East End of Long Island. You can expect to find 8 Hands Farm Egg Sandwiches, Greenport Harbor Brewery beer batter dipped fish & chips, Southold School Garden Greens Salad, Grilled Cheese Sandwiches stuffed with LI Mushroom fungi and much, much more at this delicious and unique truck.
name: North Fork Food Truck
